title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-05-2014 WED
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show FEB-05-2014 WED.....PODCAST



The Glenn Beck Program - 2/5/14Wednesday, February 05, 2014



The Glenn Beck Program is Live Monday - Friday from 9am - 12pm ET





Glenn is concerned as the militarization of police forces 
    across the county continues, 
      and troubling words from Supreme Court Justice Anton Scalia 
        indicate oppression of the people is not a far fetched theory.

  Also, technology is moving at an exponential pace,
     which may seem like a positive thing, 
       but not in reality as it could lead to the end of the human race, Glen explains.

  Plus, if you make an annual salary of $21k or more, Obama is coming for you.
